rwg BYrau, Gr 1 iv`c gurU Arjndyv jI dI bwxI[
Akwl purK ie`k hY Aqy siqgurU dI ikrpw nwl imldw hY[
(qyrI ieh k`cI g`l hY ik) prmwqmw ny hor swrIAW iQ`qW lWBy rihx id`qIAW,
Aqy (BwdroN vdI) AStmI iQ`q nUM aus ny jnm ilAw ]1]
Btkxw dy kwrn kurwhy pey hoey hy mnu`K! qUM ieh k`cIAW g`lW kr irhw hYN (ik prmwqmw ny BwdroN vdI AStmI nUM ikRSn-rUp ivc jnm ilAw)[
prmwqmw jMmx mrn qoN pry hY ]1] rhwau]
pMjIr bxw ky qUM lukw ky (Awpxy v`loN prmwqmw nUM ikRSn-mUrqI dy rUp ivc) KvWdw hYN[
hy r`b qoN tu`ty hoey mUrK! prmwqmw nwh jMmdw hY nwh mrdw hY ]2]
qUM (ikRSn-mUrqI nUM) lorI dyNdw hYN (Awpxy vloN qUM prmwqmw nUM lorI dyNdw hYN, qyrw ieh kMm) swry AprwDW (dw mUl hY)[
sV jwey (qyrw) auh mUMh ijs dI rwhIN qUM AwKdw hYN ik mwlk-pRBU jUnW ivc AwauNdw hY ]3]
prmwqmw nwh jMmdw hY nwh mrdw hY, nwh AwauNdw hY nwh jWdw hY[
auh nwnk dw prmwqmw sB QweIN ivAwpk hY ]4]1]
xxx
jdoN koeI mnu`K ieauN smJ lYNdw hY (ik prmwqmw hI sB dw rwKw hY) qW auh auTdw bYTdw hr vyly Awqmk AwnMd mwxdw hY[
qdoN aus nUM iksy iksm dw koeI (mOq Awidk dw) fr poh nhIN skdw; ]1]
AsW jIvW dw rwKw iek mwlk-pRBU hI hY[
swfw auh mwlk sB jIvW dy idl dI jwxn vwlw hY ]1] rhwau]
(jdoN mnu`K ieh smJ lYNdw hY ik iek prmwqmw hI sB jIvW dw rwKw hY) qW auh mnu`K insicMq ho ky sONdw hY insicMq ho ky jwgdw hY,
(qdoN mnu`K hr vyly ieh AwKx l`g pYNdw hY ik hy suAwmI!) qUM pRBU hI hr QW mOjUd hYN ]2]
auh mnu`K Awpxy Gr ivc (BI) suKI v`sdw hY, auh GroN bwhr (jw ky) BI AwnMd mwxdw hY,
hy nwnk! gurU ny ijs mnu`K dy ihrdy ivc (ieh) aupdyS p`kw kr id`qw (ik prmwqmw hI AsW sB jIvW dw rwKw hY) ]3]2]
xxx
nwh mYN (ihMdU dy) vrqW dw Awsrw lYNdw hW, nwh mYN (muslmwn dy) rmzwn dy mhIny (ivc r`Ky roizAW dw)[
mYN qW (isr&) aus prmwqmw nUM ismrdw hW ijhVw Aw^ir (hryk dI) r`iKAw krdw hY ]1]
myrw qW isr& auh hY (ijs nUM ihMdU) gusweIN (AwKdw hY Aqy ijs nUM muslmwn) A`lw (AwKdw hY)[
(Awqmk jIvn dI AgvweI dy sMbMD ivc) mYN ihMdU Aqy qurk dohW nwloN hI sWJ mukw leI hY ]1] rhwau]
mYN nwh kwby dw h`j krn jWdw hW (ijvyN muslmwn jWdy hn), nwh mYN (ihMdUAW vWg) qIrQW qy pUjw krn jWdw hW[
mYN qW isr& ie`k prmwqmw nUM ismrdw hW, iksy hor dUjy nUM nhIN (ismrdw) ]2]
mYN nwh (ihMdUAW vWg vyd-) pUjw krdw hW, nwh (muslmwn vWg) inmwz pVHdw hW[
mYN qW isr& inrMkwr nUM ihrdy ivc vsw ky (aus A`gy) isr invWdw hW ]3]
(Awqmk jIvn dI AgvweI vwsqy) nwh AsIN ihMdU (dy muQwj) hW, nwh AsIN muslmwn (dy muQwj) hW[
swfy ieh srIr swfI ieh ijMd (aus prmwqmw) dy id`qy hoey hn (ijs nUM muslmwn) A`lw (AwKdw hY, ijs nUM ihMdU) rwm (AwKdw hY) ]4]
hy kbIr! mYN qW ieh g`l KolH ky d`sdw hW,
ik mYN Awpxy gurU-pIr nUM iml ky Awpxy Ksm-pRBU nwl fUMGI sWJ pw r`KI hY ]5]3]
