(sMq jnW dI shwieqw nwl, swD sMgq dI brkiq nwl) Awqmk Afolqw ivc itk ky mYN dsy ihrnIAW (ieMdRIAW) bMnH ky lY AWdIAW (v`s ivc kr leIAW)[
kdy ^qw nwh Kwx vwly gur-Sbd-qIrW nwl mYN pMj (kwmwidk) ihrn (BI) ivMnH ley ]1]
sMq jnW nUM nwl lY ky mYN iSkwr Kyfx cVH ipAw (swD sMgq ivc itk ky mYN kwmwidk ihrnW nUM PVn leI iqAwrI kr leI)[
ibnw GoiVAW qoN ibnw hiQAwrW qoN (auh kwmwidk) ihrn mYN PV ley (v`s ivc kr ley) ]1] rhwau]
(swD sMgq dI brkiq nwl, sMq jnW dI shwieqw nwl) ivSy-ivkwrW dw iSkwr Kyfx vwlw suBwau (myry AMdroN) dOV ky bwhr inkl igAw[
(ijs mn nUM pkVnw sI auh mn-) iSkwr mYnUM Awpxy srIr dy AMdr hI l`B ipAw (qy, mYN aus nUM kwbU kr ilAw) ]2]
(pMjW) ihrnW nUM PV ky mYN Awpxy Gr ivc lY AWdw, AwpxI h`tI ivc lY AWdw[
(sMq jn auhnW nUM) rqw rqw kr ky (myry AMdroN) dUr-durwfy QW lY gey (myry AMdroN sMq jnW ny pMjW kwmwidk ihrnW nUM au~kw hI k`F id`qw) ]3]
sMq jnW ny ieh PiVAw hoieAw iSkwr (ieh v`s ivc kIqw hoieAw myrw mn) mYnUM b^SIS dy qOr qy dy id`qw[
hux mYN nwnk dy ihrdy ivc isr& prmwqmw dw nwm hI nwm hY (mn v`s ivc Aw igAw hY, qy kwmwidk BI Awpxw zor nhIN pw skdy) ]4]4]
