prmwqmw qoN tu`ty hoey mnu`K nUM jy sO vwrI BI bVI qWG nwl (aus dw Awqmk jIvn kwiem r`Kx leI nwm-) Bojn Kvwlx dw jqn kIqw jwey,
qW BI aus dy ic`q ivc prmwqmw dw nwm (-Bojn) itk nhIN skdw ]1]
(prmwqmw dy crnW nwloN tu`ty hoey bMidAW dI sMgq krn dy QW) sMq jnW pwsoN (shI jIvn-jugiq dI) is`iKAw ilAw kro[
sMq jnW dI sMgq ivc (rih ky) qusIN sB qoN au~cI Awqmk AvsQw pRwpq kr lvogy ]1] rhwau]
jy iksy p`Qr au~qy bhuq swrw pwxI sutwieAw jwey, (qW BI auh p`Qr AMdroN) iB`jdw nhIN,
(AMdroN auh) iblkul su`kw hI rihMdw hY (iehI hwl hY swkq dw) ]2]
